OL,3,CMan with mobility issues has walking
OL,4,Cstick confiscated at airport
OL,6,FHowever, on this occasion, Robin says
OL,7,Fsecurity staff were "very aggressive",
OL,8,Ftold him it was a banned item and took
OL,9,Fit off him.
OL,11,FRobin explains: "The reason I need the
OL,12,Fstick is that I have balance problems
OL,13,Fand if I turn suddenly, I often wobble
OL,14,Fand look like I'm drunk. To me, it's
OL,15,Fabsolutely vital."
OL,17,FHe wants to raise awareness so that
OL,18,Fothers are not caught out and is
OL,19,Fcalling for common sense.
